key|value|description
backend.baseUrl|http://localhost:8080|Default local Spring Boot backend URL
frontend.baseUrl|http://localhost:3000|Default local Next.js website URL
selenium.browser|chrome|Default Selenium browser
selenium.headless|true|Run browser headless in CI
appium.serverUrl|http://127.0.0.1:4723|Default local Appium server URL
appium.deviceName|Android Emulator|Default Android emulator name
appium.platformName|Android|Mobile platform name
appium.automationName|UiAutomator2|Android automation engine
appium.appPackage|com.kingsparkon.tracker|Placeholder Android package name
appium.appActivity|.MainActivity|Placeholder Android launch activity
barcode.sample|6009801234567|Seeded barcode value for tests
worker.sampleId|1001|Seeded worker ID for scanner tests
